Package: butlerrr
Type: Package
Title: Helper and Convenience Functions for Recurring Coding Operations
Version: 0.1.0
Description: The goal of butlerrr is to provide helper and convenience (hence the name) functions for some recurring R coding operations.
    These include, but not limited to operations with symbols, calls, functions, strings etc.
